longBusinessSummary: Damaris SA offers tools and services for documents. Its product portfolio includes Damaris RM, a record management application that manage various legal document types, such as pay slip, customer invoice, supplier invoice, and proof of delivery; Damaris mobile application; Damaris printer, a Microsoft Windows standard printer driver; and Damaris scan manager application that manages various scanning projects. The company was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Dardilly, France.
